item.title: CoreUI Free React.js Admin Template v5.0.0-rc.1 (Vite)
item.description: We’re delighted to announce the release of CoreUI Free React.js Admin Template v5.0.0-rc.1 on March 22, 2024. This update signifies a pivotal advancement in our effort to provide the most efficient, modern, and developer-friendly admin template. Focused on enhancing performance, usability, and developer experience, this release incorporates significant feature upgrades, refactorings, and dependency updates.
